				<mj-image
					src="https://team-switch-reclamebureau.github.io/dfg-newsletter/public/25/07/2.png"
					href="https://team-switch-reclamebureau.github.io/dfg-newsletter/public/25/07/in-the-spotlights-jonny-young.pdf?utm_source=mail&utm_medium=mail&utm_campaign=nieuwsbrief&utm_term=july_25&utm_content=flipbook"
					alt=""
				/>
				<mj-text mj-class="">
					Jonny Young is joining the DFG Sustainability Team as
					Project Lead Sustainability – Social, where he will be
					leading the group’s work on social and human rights. What
					will be his focus and what does he need from other DFG
					colleagues?
				</mj-text>
				<mj-image
					width="291px"
					align="left"
					src="https://team-switch-reclamebureau.github.io/dfg-newsletter/public/button/read-more.png"
