		<mj-section padding="0 20px">
			<mj-column width="100%" padding="10px 20px">
				<mj-text mj-class="title-2"
					>Wellbeing of our People: Boost Yourself</mj-text
				>
				<mj-image
					src="https://team-switch-reclamebureau.github.io/dfg-newsletter/public/25/07/3.png"
					href="https://werkenbijdfg.nl/en/boost-yourself/boost-together?utm_source=mail&utm_medium=mail&utm_campaign=nieuwsbrief&utm_term=july_25&utm_content=flipbook"
					alt=""
				/>
				<mj-text mj-class="">
					To contribute to the pillar ‘Wellbeing of our People,’ work
					has been underway since the beginning of this year to
					develop the ‘Boost Yourself’ program. With Boost Yourself,
					we aim to get our employees moving – both literally and
					figuratively. The program consists of four components:
					<ul>
						<li>
							BOOST Samen (Together) – Strengthen your team spirit
							and enjoyment at work with fun and engaging
							activities.
						</li>
						<li>
							BOOST Next – Develop yourself as an employee and
							discover new talents for the future with workshops
							and assessments.
						</li>
						<li>
							BOOST Focus – Find mental calm and take control of
							your energy with training sessions, scans, and even
							break reminders.
						</li>
						<li>
							BOOST Fit – Prevent or resolve physical discomfort
							with smart tools and targeted workplace advice.
						</li>
					</ul>
					Please not that this is not a mandatory program or imposed
					plan, but rather a set of personal choices. Please take some
					time to look at our ‘Boost Yourself’ website and learn more
					about all the different boosts.
				</mj-text>
				<mj-image
					width="333px"
					align="left"
					src="https://team-switch-reclamebureau.github.io/dfg-newsletter/public/button/boost-yourself.png"
					href="https://werkenbijdfg.nl/en/boost-yourself/boost-together/?utm_source=mail&utm_medium=mail&utm_campaign=nieuwsbrief&utm_term=july_25&utm_content=flipbook"
					alt=""
					padding="0"
